original_title: It Isn't Easy Being Azealia Banks
overview: In partnership with Well Being Trust, Complex created a mini documentary on Banks’ journey towards recognition, redemption, and self-actualization in the face of mental health tribulations. Get a deep look inside the life of one of pop music’s most controversial figures, one who is beautiful and flawed, just like the rest of us
title: It Isn't Easy Being Azealia Banks
